        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">cascadas</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">naturaleza</span>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">parque</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4"><h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900 mb-1">📍 Dirección</h4><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Parque Nacional Vicente Perez Rosales, Puerto Varas</p></div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900 mb-1">💰 Precio</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">$</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4"><h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900 mb-1">👥 Ideal para</h4><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">naturaleza</p></div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4"><h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-gray-900 mb-1">🗓️ Temporada</h4><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">todo-el-año</p></div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100 rounded-xl p-4"><h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-purple-900 mb-1">💡 Tip local</h4><p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">Comprar entrada online evita la fila en temporada alta.</p></div>
        <a href="https://tucorretaje.cl" target="_blank" class="block text-center text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-xl no-underline hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity" style="background: #6D28D9;">🏠 Ver propiedades en puerto varas</a>
